{"tid":1319212,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[戰術討論] 琴日發夢守源禾路三條防線嘅入一入來！","createTime":"2019-07-15T06:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T04:06:40.000Z","uid":30205,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"edc54ba727e9a0732a3429ec6d794236004ed072","tid":1319212,"uid":30205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"想同發夢上前線嘅朋友討論吓戰術<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">防線唔係越多越前就好 陣地亦都唔係越大越好！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我發夢見到好多前線兄弟都好熱心 一見到對面班狗有動作就開始拆鐵馬set防線 但屌你老母可唔可以睇吓地型先set呀！<br />\n<br />\n金鐘 <br />\n同一條馬路可以有三 四條防線 但另一邊可能封得個頭又唔封埋個尾<br />\n<br />\n沙田 <br />\n琴日仲on9 十字路口開三點防線 仲要距離不一 萬一其中一點畀人突破到只會<strong>陷家剷！</strong><br />\n與其分散人力要同時守三點 點解唔集中守一點 就算你玩hit&amp;run都易啲！ 自己諗吓<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">三倍風險 但防守除返三</span><br />\n<br />\n依家唔撚係叫你地撤或者走 係應該更有系統同戰略咁同班狗對抗 <br />\n為咗贏就更加唔應該浪費人力物力 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">裝備唔夠人強 就要智取！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n721夢中再見！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"667f0fc50f136256fb4874de76e9636562394ad2","tid":1319212,"uid":30205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:07:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f635eb996248db4435c26d3ae00d18d4fc7c82ce","tid":1319212,"uid":30205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:07:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd01f8d4ec40c25e935cf02063aa41985757d6c","tid":1319212,"uid":30205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T06:08:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6862238d9ac0928d5335661993443